.offer-select
  .offer-select__title
    オファーを出す案件を選択してください
  .offer-select__select-box
    = form_with(url: "/users/#{@user.id}/offers", local: true, method: :post, class: "search-form") do |f|
      = f.collection_select :matter_id, @matters, :id, :title, prompt: "---"
      %br
      = f.submit "この案件でオファーを出す"
      %br


